HEADWORD: Colymbiformes
<hw>Colymbiformes</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>an order of birds,
including the family <fam>Podicipedidae</fam>, which constitutes the
grebes.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> Podicipitiformes, order <ord>Podicipitiformes</ord>,
Podicipediformes, order <ord>Podicipediformes</ord>, order
<ord>Colymbiformes</ord>.</syn>⟦br⟧
